<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Privacy Policy | LifeSystemOS</title>
<meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for LifeSystemOS. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://lifesystemos.com/privacy-policy.html">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#0c0a1d;color:#f1f5f9;line-height:1.8;padding:2rem}
.container{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto}
h1{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d9488,#14b8a6);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
h2{color:#14b8a6;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;font-size:1.2rem}
p{color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:0.938rem}
a{color:#14b8a6}
.back{margin-bottom:2rem;display:inline-block;color:#14b8a6;text-decoration:none}
.back:hover{text-decoration:underline}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<a href="/" class="back">&larr; Back to LifeSystemOS</a>
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>Last updated: June 4, 2026</p>
<p>LifeSystemOS respects your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>
<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when subscribing to our newsletter (name and email address). We also collect anonymous analytics data through Plausible Analytics, which does not use cookies.</p>
<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use your email to send you newsletter updates, productivity tips, and occasional promotional content. You can unsubscribe at any time. Analytics data is used solely to improve our content and user experience.</p>
<h2>Data Protection</h2>
<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. We do not sell, trade, or share your data with third parties except as required by law.</p>
<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For privacy-related questions, please contact us through our website.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
